[div class=p 
	"You can delay scroll into this stage from the end of the Heat fight (whether this can be done Buster Only remains to be seen). If you do, the collision is super glitchy, and you can sort of wall jump on this building. With this tech, you can make it quite a bit further. But even if you could make it all the way to the dragon and 
	[a href=https://youtu.be/jiJEbXHmvDY?t=66 rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"survive its giant fart
	]a
	", it would just count as defeating Heat Man. Plus, I don't know of a way to load the real Wily 1 in this state, but I do know this 
	[a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zyLfi-dqJas rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"cool softlock
	]a
	". So... yeah.
	$LF
